# CFSetGetTypeID()

**Function**

Returns the type identifier for the CFSet type.

## Declaration

```swift
func CFSetGetTypeID() -> CFTypeID
```

## Return Value

The type identifier for the CFSet type.

## Discussion

CFMutableSet has the same type identifier as CFSet.
